            31.7653502,-25.3928128,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Stone Circle Backpackers</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Stone Circle Backpackers offers rustic accommodation in traditional rondavels and camping sites, some with shared bathrooms. The hostel features a communal kitchen, braai area, and outdoor pool. Free WiFi is available. Apart from the usual attractions, guests have the unique opportunity to join tours of ancient sites led by author Michael Tellinger. These tours provide fascinating insights into the region's rich archaeological history, exploring the mysteries of the stone circles and other ancient structures scattered throughout the Mpumalanga region. It's an extraordinary chance to delve into the past and uncover the secrets of these enigmatic sites.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1603-FFD600</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            30.3297941,-25.6391094,0
