      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Goldrush Backpackers</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Goldrush Backpackers offers comfortable accommodation in dormitories and private rooms, some with en-suite bathrooms. The hostel features a communal kitchen, bar, and outdoor terrace. Free WiFi is provided. Local attractions include visiting the nearby gold mining towns of Pilgrim's Rest and Barberton, exploring the scenic Panorama Route, and wildlife viewing in the nearby Kruger National Park.]]></description>
