      <Placemark>
        <name>Bundu Bashers Inn</name>
        <description>Bundu Bashers Inn provides budget-friendly accommodation in dormitories and private rooms with shared bathrooms. The inn offers a communal kitchen, lounge area, and outdoor braai facilities. Free WiFi is available. Nearby attractions include exploring the iSimangaliso Wetland Park, birdwatching in the nearby Ukuwela Conservancy, and visiting the Zulu cultural villages.</description>
