      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Saint Lucia Backpackers</name>
        <description>Saint Lucia Backpackers offers affordable accommodation in dormitories and private rooms, some with en-suite bathrooms. The hostel features a communal kitchen, lounge area, and outdoor terrace with BBQ facilities. Free WiFi is provided. Local attractions include boat cruises on the St Lucia Estuary, guided tours of the iSimangaliso Wetland Park, and hiking trails in the nearby Eastern Shores.</description>
