      <Placemark>
        <name>Stokkiesdraai Holiday Accommodation</name>
        <description>Stokkiesdraai offers rustic accommodation in safari tents and chalets, some with shared bathrooms. The camp features a communal kitchen, dining area, and outdoor boma. Free WiFi is provided. Nearby attractions include game drives in the nearby Hluhluwe-iMfolozi Park, boat cruises on the St Lucia Estuary, and cultural experiences with the local Zulu communities.</description>
