      <Placemark>
        <name>Amadwala Lodge</name>
        <description>Amadwala Lodge, situated in the serene outskirts of Johannesburg, offers a range of accommodations including safari tents and cozy chalets. The lodge features amenities such as free WiFi, a swimming pool, a restaurant, and a bar. Nestled in a natural setting, guests can enjoy activities like hiking and bird watching, while still being close to city attractions.</description>
